  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      What are the effects of the currently used AEDs on bone mineralization in children and
      adolescents between the ages of 8 to 18? This is a pilot observational study using DEXA scans
      to measure bone mineral density in 100 patients The primary objective is to collect
      preliminary data on bone mineral density, body weight, dietary calcium intake, and activity
      level.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
